      <title>霍华德大学因卡西被袭击视频而与肖恩·“吹牛老爹”·科姆斯断绝关系</title>
      <link>https://apnews.com/article/diddy-howard-university-degree-rescinded-6d8a2df95faa00d36149d34c6d4c51e1</link>
